msgid "1. Global Configuration"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/introduction.md:24
msgid "First, the following must be defined:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/introduction.md:25
msgid "Which constituencies exist"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/introduction.md:26
msgid "Which parties participate in the election"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/introduction.md:27
msgid "How large the government majority should be"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/introduction.md:28
msgid ""
"Whether constituencies should be represented by the entire parliament or "
"only by the government majority. **Note**: This determines the size of "
"parliament. For details see [Global "
"Configuration](global_configuration.md)"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/introduction.md:30
msgid "2. Iterative Proportional Representation with Guaranteed Winner"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/en/introduction.md:31
msgid ""
"An iterative proportional vote is conducted that guarantees a winning "
"party or coalition. For details see [Iterative Proportional "
"Representation](iterative_proportional_election.md)"
msgstr ""

